title: High school boys soccer: Wheaton Academy, Wheaton North, Wheaton Warrenville South Boys set for postseason
text:
Sectional seed: No. 11 
First match: 6:30 p.m. Oct. 20 vs. No. 7 Addison Trail 
Outlook: The Tigersâ€™ record may not look impressive (6-12-2 as of Oct. 13), but they are more than ready for the rigors of the state playoffs. They faced three No. 1 playoff seeds this season (Crystal Lake South, Warren and Naperville North) and also challenged themselves against traditional powers New Trier, St. Charles North and Neuqua Valley. Addison Trail is first up in the postseason. With a win WWS would advance to the regional final Oct. 24.
